# - Find Mujin Controller Client C++ Library
#
# Users can set the following variables before calling the module:
#  MujinPlanningClient_DIR - The preferred installation prefix for searching for MujinPlanningClient. Set by the user.
#
# MujinPlanningClient_ROOT_DIR - the root directory where the installation can be found
# MujinPlanningClient_CXX_FLAGS - extra flags for compilation
# MujinPlanningClient_LINK_FLAGS - extra flags for linking
# MujinPlanningClient_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directories
# MujinPlanningClient_LIBRARY_DIRS - link directories
# MujinPlanningClient_LIBRARIES - libraries to link plugins with
# MujinPlanningClient_Boost_VERSION - the boost version was compiled with

